ygData.messageBody:
You must find the docks in Butcherblock. From the dwarven city of Kaladim,
looking out from the gates toward the path, follow the path to your right.
It will take you to the docks where you can wait for the boat. After you
board the boat, Freeport is the third stop.

Talarin Kal'Amon, High Elven WIzard
